\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Sarah:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Sarah starts the scene alone in her bedroom regretful about breaking a promise and replying to texts and emails when she said she wouldn't. She was severely disappointed in herself for displaying such low integrity. Her father's voice inside her head reverberated a message he had repeated hundreds of times. "Without your integrity, your nothing." Sarah felt like nothing at this moment. As much as she didn't want to do it, especially in front of Evan's sister, her strong moral compass compelled her to follow the only path to redemption. That is to confess what she did to Evan in front of Liz.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Evan:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Evan was fully recovered from his minute of disappointment when he had correctly guessed that Sarah was working while he and Liz were setting up. He was touched and impressed that Sarah, of her own accord, admitted that she was working when she shouldn't have been. Honesty goes a long way with Evan. Her honesty definitely one of supports and turned a misstep into a positive outcome.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Liz:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> After learning a few things about Sarah from Evan, she felt this a be a good opportunity to comfort Sarah and let her know that she is already part of the family. She does this one Evan and Joe are teaming up to bring in the turkey. It's a private moment between women..<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
